        "description": "<p><em>Sports!</em> is an educational sports game for one to four players. It's aimed at children ages 4-7 years and teaches five skills of mathematics: addition, number recognition, patterns, shapes and subtraction. The game contains nine mini-games most of which are played with motion controls. The games can be played on their own or as part of an event challenge which consists of four events where the player earns a medal for each event. The mini-games included are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Super Goalie</li>\n<li>Karate</li>\n<li>Baseball</li>\n<li>Bowling</li>\n<li>Swimming</li>\n<li>Rope Climbing</li>\n<li>Weightlifting</li>\n<li>Skateboarding</li>\n<li>Snowboarding</li>\n</ul>",
